{"tid":2227883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★港鐵怪男狂咳呃位坐？ 戴穿窿口罩惹播毒恐慌","createTime":"2020-10-03T06:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T07:50:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3ffb44b6201b008b610faeb276b9efa07509933c","tid":2227883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Up6MQ5dLj2g0VnJbGH.hrQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/0186ac20-0514-11eb-adff-38ba099002a3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUp6MQ5dLj2g0VnJbGH.hrQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F0186ac20-0514-11eb-adff-38ba099002a3&h=fcb625e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民Seth Li日前(30日)在Facebook貼文，講述在港鐵車廂中遇見該名男子經過。對方戴着破裂的口罩站在通道位置，但就刻意向着在座位上乘客咳嗽。目擊者形容，「呢個男人口罩穿嘅，唔知傻定咩，對住原本坐低嗰啲人係咁咳，咳到全部人散開，佢坐低又冇見再咳...希望唔會係第4波散播者...」。從目擊者分享相片可見，男子身穿恤衫西褲，打扮如一般上班族，但所戴口罩就顯得十分殘舊，中間部分更是裂開，根本無防疫作用。<br />\n<br />\n網民看到貼文後，都分享自己遇見怪男的經歷，「見佢喺太和上車，街坊小心」、「我見過佢幾次，佢到九龍塘未埋站就橫衝直撞去門口，借開都唔會講」。不過有想法正面的網民為其解說，「係咪有困難呀，佢連件恤衫都好似唔啱身。如果有多口罩送個畀有需要嘅人啦。」亦有網民幽默回應：「醒目呀，咳兩咳就有位坐！」<br />\n<br />\n網民有話說：<br />\n<br />\nEcho Hong：個口罩似係用咗幾日，啲口水溶咗個罩，好惡心<br />\n<br />\nC.m. Yin：佢想有位坐，特登咁做<br />\n<br />\nSuny Kon：佢再咳就兜口兜面噴佢酒精<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%80%AA%E7%94%B7%E7%8B%82%E5%92%B3%E5%91%83%E4%BD%8D%E5%9D%90-%E6%88%B4%E7%A9%BF%E7%AA%BF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%83%B9%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C-010206240.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E6%2580%25AA%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%258B%2582%25E5%2592%25B3%25E5%2591%2583%25E4%25BD%258D%25E5%259D%2590-%25E6%2588%25B4%25E7%25A9%25BF%25E7%25AA%25BF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E6%2583%25B9%25E6%2592%25AD%25E6%25AF%2592%25E6%2581%2590%25E6%2585%258C-010206240.html&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=8ed1bde5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%80%AA%E7%94%B7%E7%8B%82%E5%92%B3%E5%91%83%E4%BD%8D%E5%9D%90-%E6%88%B4%E7%A9%BF%E7%AA%BF%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E6%83%B9%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92%E6%81%90%E6%85%8C-010206240.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c256d00ed0e0e087b0194fcfcde205fd310e8ad","tid":2227883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00726bfcff0c432113995d75c9c788734f471cca","tid":2227883,"uid":40272,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qJMTEei.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqJMTEei.jpg&h=6264ba41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026bb79b37be98f85a8120440a45b3fda37737d8","tid":2227883,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"Mr.bean"},{"pid":"077ffbfecd12a57af91d25fcc54ea5a6c4cf16f4","tid":2227883,"uid":378305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T06:56:15.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意有位坐、下次自己帶張摺凳去坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56563b095eaabe5fb28f8173b57e50fcc9085620","tid":2227883,"uid":7760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":